channel.title: New project :)
channel.description:
hey everyone, its xmonster here. starting a new project. going to be recreating actual runescape 07 or around there :D. ok so this will be just like runescape with all the features coded.
Features ~~
Duel arena, castlewars, bounty hunter, god wars, no customs, all members stuff, all warning sign interfaces while entering dangerous zones, clan wars, and so much more! the economy will be similar to runescape, we will try to get as close as runescapes npcdrops as possible. all the shops will be accurate to runescape. Many others that im planning to add!
The website will be old runescape website also. I think this would be a cool thing to create so please dont flame :)! I plan to work on this for a very long time! i will release after 1 month of hosting! I will continue with this project!
Web developer 1/1 GFX designer 1/2 (must create runescape logo) Server developers 1/4
